# Pre-Action Checklist

1. New shared string or timeout → `src/utils/constants.ts`.
2. Reuse helpers in page objects before adding new ones.
3. Arrow functions, strict typing, no `any`.
4. Specs stay free of raw locators and direct `expect` on locators — use page objects.
5. Prettier: single quotes, trailing commas, width 100.
